  "text": "This Post May Contain Affiliate Links. Please Read Our Disclosure Policy here If you’ve been a blog reader for a long time or maybe you read Love the Home You Have or saw my post about my new Dreambook, you probably know I’m a dreamer and a fairytale believer—especially when it comes to homes and happily-ever-afters. So it may not be a surprise to you that I would enjoy making these Beatrix Potter style illustrations of the storybook life I dream about! Naturally, since my stove is named after Beatrix Potter, it felt right. Creating these illustrations has been a fun new trend on Instagram lately, so I thought you all would love them as much as I do! Want to make one, too? You can create them with ChatGPT (add an image and ask it to make it into a Beatrix Potter style illustration!)! Happy weekend, friends! Never grow up and never stop dreaming! +++++++++ If you are a kindred spirit who loves cottages by the sea and dreaming of homes like I do, be sure to get your Cottage by the Sea Spring Dreambook here! And, I would love it if you would join us in our HomeBody community so we can create real life homes together.",
